ActCanada Post Corporation Act
SubjectRegulations Amending Certain Regulations Made Under the Canada Post Corporation Act (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations Amending CERTAIN REGULATIONS MADE UNDER THE CANADA POST CORPORATION ACT (Miscellaneous Program) are technical in nature and ensure that Canada Post's regulations are consistent with the latest Universal Postal Convention. They also ensure that the French and English versions are consistent.
